        {
            "+content": "Hareluya Hibino is a freshman at Rakuen High School who has only one goal in life: World Domination. Luckily, while that goal makes him extremely arrogant, rude, & uncaring on the outside, Hareluya is also very benevolent & willing to help those who are need of assistance. Along with his friends Kiyoshiro, who wants to become a painter, Yamana, who wants to be a jewelry designer, & Ichijou, who wants to be a rock star, Hareluya is ready to take on all comers, whether it's dirty baseball players from a rival school, corrupt businessmen, underground fighters, & all sorts of crazy delinquents.",
